303
00:16:06,799 --> 00:16:07,808
Let me go.

304
00:16:08,640 --> 00:16:10,896
Let me go!

305
00:16:14,960 --> 00:16:16,220
You didn't hear that?

306
00:16:16,719 --> 00:16:18,112
She said let her go.

307
00:16:20,280 --> 00:16:21,960
Hey, hey.

308
00:16:21,960 --> 00:16:24,120
