359
00:19:44,880 --> 00:19:46,800
I just have no time to throw it.

360
00:19:47,280 --> 00:19:48,660
I'll return to you now.

361
00:19:49,839 --> 00:19:52,160
Professor Zhuang, you're handsome today.

362
00:19:52,160 --> 00:19:54,704
